verbose_text: The major results of the present study were as follows : i) An inverse association between SG formation and apoptotic level was identified in MCAO rats; ii) miR-335 was decreased in the MCAO rats and the mRNA of ROCK2 was the effective target of miR-335; and iii) the SG formation promoted by miR-335 inhibits apoptosis levels by inhibiting ROCK2 expression in AIS.
